    dc:date "2021" ;
    dc:title "One Hundred Years of Solitude: rediscovery of Catasticta lycurgus (Godman & Salvin, 1880), a yellow butterfly from the Sierra Nevada de Santa Marta, Colombia (Lepidoptera: Pieridae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4806002>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4806008>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4806012> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4806002>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. a. Original figure of Euterpe lycurgus from Godman & Salvin (1880). b. Holotype, male specimen dorsal view and labels c. ventral view (B. Huertas, Trustees NHMUK)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4806002/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4806008>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. New male specimens known of C. lycurgus. a. recently collected dorsal view. b. ventral view (M. Bollino) c. female of C. lycurgus illustrated for the first time, dorsal view d. ventral view (C. Prieto) f. male genitalia (M. Bollino)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4806008/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4806012>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. a. Map showing the known collecting localities of C. lycurgus in Colombia. b. forest habitat in San Pedro de la Sierra, road to Las Lagunas at 2,600 m (F. Montero) c-d. live specimens of C. lycurgus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4806012/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

